Pets.name: Spot
Pets.description: Playful, affectionate, fun-loving companions. They have a great zest for life.

Pets.name: Ralph
Pets.description: Friendly and intelligent but somewhat independent and stubborn. They need firm, gentle training from puppyhood.

Pets.name: Lucky
Pets.description: Outgoing, trustworthy, and eager-to-please family dogs, and relatively easy to train.

Pets.name: Puffy
Pets.description: Independent, dignified, and aloof in general, but they are affectionate and extremely loyal to humans they have bonded with.

Pets.name: Fluffy
Pets.description: Loyal, confident, courageous, and steady, the German Shepherd is truly a dog lover's delight.

Pets.name: Blinky
Pets.description: Never fierce or intractable, but always refined and dignified. Serene and adaptable, they happily take to city life.

Pets.name: Cheddar
Pets.description: Strong, athletic, and lively little herder who is affectionate and companionable without being needy.

Pets.name: Daisy
Pets.description: Known for their playful personality and their calm and friendly temperament.

Pets.name: Chase
Pets.description: Muscular, with a soft and loose coat forming wrinkles.
